OL,3,CDog walker pushes through barriers at
OL,4,Clevel crossing as train slams on brakes
OL,6,FCCTV from a level crossing in has
OL,7,Fcaught the moment a dog walker pushes
OL,8,Fthrough the barriers to cross the
OL,9,Ftracks - with a train slamming on the
OL,10,Fbrakes just moments after.
OL,12,Freleased the footage of the near miss
OL,13,Ffrom the Blakedown crossing as a
OL,14,Fsafety warning to people who might
OL,15,Fattempt the same.
OL,17,FCaught on camera at 10:27am on Tuesday
OL,18,F13 February, the pedestrian shoved the
OL,19,Fsafety barriers out of the way and
OL,20,Fwalked across the tracks with their
OL,21,Fdog in tow.
