OL,6,FShe continued: "I'd like to use this
OL,7,Fvideo as a reminder to anyone who uses
OL,8,Flevel crossings to do so safely. No
OL,9,Fmatter how well you think you know a
OL,10,Fcrossing, all users must obey the
OL,11,Fsafety systems in place such as lights
OL,12,Fand barriers which are there to
OL,13,Fprotect the communities we serve.
OL,15,F"When crossing the railway, I'd urge
OL,16,Fpeople to think about their own safety
OL,17,Fas well as the impact their actions
OL,18,Fcould have on their family, the wider
OL,19,Fcommunity and train drivers. It really
OL,20,Fisn't worth the risk."
