OL,6,FIt's not the first time the Blakedown
OL,7,Flevel crossing has been misused. In
OL,8,F2017, Network Rail released another
OL,9,Fvideo of a young person running across
OL,10,Fthe tracks and diving under the
OL,11,Fbarriers just before they fully
OL,12,Flowered.
OL,14,FOfficials described the individual's
OL,15,Factions as "selfish", with "little
OL,16,Frespect for his own safety or the
OL,17,Fsafety of others by doing this
OL,18,Firresponsible act."
OL,20,FPictures from Network Rail.
