OL,6,FThe health and safety director at West
OL,7,FMidlands Railway, Jamie Ainsworth,
OL,8,Fsaid regarding the recent incident:
OL,9,F"The safety of the general public, our
OL,10,Fcustomers and colleagues is always our
OL,11,Fpriority and incidents such as this
OL,12,Fare hugely alarming which could have
OL,13,Fhad catastrophic consequences.
OL,15,F"I hope this video will remind the
OL,16,Fpublic to concentrate, wait behind
OL,17,Fbarriers and follow instructions at
OL,18,Flevel crossings to stay safe at all
OL,19,Ftimes.
